She chuckles,"WHy thanks you. It's the latest fashion from the 
Predacon Empire. You like?" she put both hands on her hips and stood 
next to him. "You know, I think I wear this stuff better than the 
ship does."  She took her finger and touched Striker's nose, leaving 
a black mark on his nose.  "Your not bad looking in black yourself." 
chuckles.
